  _missions:
  - Act: 2
    QuestId: firstTax
    Title: Twelve Silver by Yule
    Summary: Demand twelve silver and name the Wenmar cottage as security.
  - Act: 3
    QuestId: aldricLetter
    Title: A Sealed Letter
    Summary: Deliver Lord Aldric's letter to Wren in person.
  _quotes:
  - Text: I am not unsympathetic, but I am also not paid to be sympathetic.
    Context: Explaining the tax demand.
  - Text: I was already doing so.
    Context: When Wren tells him to wait for payment.
  - Text: I am not here to collect.
    Context: Returning to Hollowfen with Aldric's letter.
